title: Daredevil & Batman - Eye For An Eye (1997) (Bchry-DCP)
description:
An Elseworlds crossover tale written by Dan Chichester which sees the Dark Knight and Daredevil combine pretty effectively. Synopsis from Comicvine - "An alternate universe where Daredevil and Batman coexist. Though they do not like each other they are forced to work together to stop the combined might of Two-face and Mr. Hyde."

This is the re-done edition by Bchry-DCP about a month ago. Thanks to them for their efforts, please seed and enjoy! :-)
